data.description: New construction completed in Feb 2023 but BETTER because the back yard is fully landscaped!  This lovely home in Mtn. View Meadows offers 2,386 sf w/ 3 BRs + 2.25 baths.  Main floor offers Great Room w/ eating space plus office /den.  HUGE Bonus room upstairs! Beautiful slab quartz counters make your kitchen light and bright! And REFRIGERATOR is included.  Large island for company to gather. SS undermount sink and Shaker style cabinets. Go out the slider to your beautifully landscaped, FULLY FENCED private back yard for BBQs, or sit under the metal gazebo and enjoy the peace, quiet and lovely Mt. Rainier view! Heat pump. Close to schools, restaurants, parks, amenities and only 15 minutes to JBLM. Truly Move-In Ready.
